ATTR_INDICATOR_NOTE_OF_SOURCE: This indicator notes whether a country is or is not a member of the WePROTECT Global Alliance (WPGA), a global movement that brings together companies, civil society and governments to transform how online child sexual exploitation is dealt with worldwide. Members of WeProtect Global Alliance receive support in developing national responses to online child sexual exploitation guided by theWePROTECT Model National Response to Child Sexual Exploitation and Abuse. As yet there are no reports on member countries activities, so the indicator assumes that membership of the Alliance signals a commitment to take action.

As yet there are no reports on member countries activities, so the indicator assumes that membership of the Alliance signals a commitment to take action.
